==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German [[ziohan]], from Germanic ''*tiuxan-''.  Cognate with Middle Dutch [[tien|tīen]], Old English [[teon|tēon]].

===Verb===
'''ziehen'''
# to [[pull]] (a rope)
# to get a weapon from its holster

